public class MenuBar
extends javax.swing.JMenuBar
implements java.io.Serializable, java.beans.beancontext.BeanContextMembershipListener, java.beans.beancontext.BeanContextChild

This object looks for objects implementing MenuI interface and adds them to itself. if an object implements HelpMenuI, it is then added as the last element.
